WEBVTT

00:06:59.141 --> 00:07:01.474
instead of seeing the broad picture.

00:07:01.498 --> 00:07:06.084
And I'm afraid to say
that with algorithms, with logarithms,

00:07:06.108 --> 00:07:07.756
with whatever the "-ithms" are

00:07:07.780 --> 00:07:12.046
that direct us into all these particular
channels of information,

00:07:12.070 --> 00:07:13.940
that seems to be happening right now.

00:07:13.964 --> 00:07:16.508
I mean, people have written
about this phenomenon.

00:07:16.532 --> 00:07:18.730
People have said that yes,
the internet came,

00:07:18.754 --> 00:07:24.497
its promise was to exponentially explode
our access to more democracy,

00:07:24.521 --> 00:07:26.235
more information,

00:07:26.259 --> 00:07:28.151
less bias,

00:07:28.175 --> 00:07:30.564
more varied information.